@node "support_modules" "support_modules"
@tab 40
@{_Title_ "Support Modules"}

@{u}ISO Lib Support Modules@{uu}@{line}
   @{b}ArgsSupport@{ub}@{tab}specification, reading, and initial parsing of command line arguments.@{line}
   @{b}TextIOHelper@{ub}@{tab}eases the use of the ISO standard TextIO input routines.@{line}

@{u}Null delimited static strings@{uu}@{line}
   @{b}Str0@{ub}@{tab}Basic procedures.@{line}
   @{b}Str1@{ub}@{tab}More procedures.@{line}

@{u}Dynamic strings@{uu}@{line}
   @{b}DynStr0@{ub}@{tab}Basic procedures, size fixed at create time.@{line}
   @{b}DynStr1@{ub}@{tab}Common procedures.@{line}
   @{b}DynStr1b@{ub}@{tab}some Strings module flavor procs.@{line}
   @{b}DynStr1NC@{ub}@{tab}Compare procedures, case insensitive.@{line}
   @{b}DynStr1C@{ub}@{tab}Common procedures, one character parameter.@{line}
   @{b}DynStr3@{ub}@{tab}As DynStr0 and DynStr1, but size will be reallocated on assignment.@{line}
   @{b}TextBlocks@{ub}@{tab}In-memory, line-oriented, dynamically-extending blocks of text.@{line}

@{u}List processing@{uu}@{line}
   @{b}ListV2Processor@{ub}@{tab}Simple generalized list processing module.@{line}

@{u}Misc@{uu}@{line}
   @{b}MaxMin@{ub}@{tab}Maximum and Minimum functions for CARDs, INTs, REALs.@{line}
   @{b}Debugging0@{ub}@{tab}Assert and Debug procs.@{line}
   @{b}TBChans@{ub}@{tab}used only by tsttgM2Parser.ts@{line}




@endnode
@node "TestManager" "TestManager"
@{_Title_ "TestManager"}

A companion program, @{i}TestManager@{ui}, has been written to act as a testing "harness". It will run automate the running of many testing in a batch mode. ie, It will take a list of *.ts scripts, run @{_tgm2_} multiple times to generate the test driver Modula-2 files, compile, link, and run them, and then give a summary report on passed and failed tests.@{line}

For example, test cases for bugs that have been fixed in the compiler are run recursively to detect any that have re-appeared via this command:


TestManager -@tg "TstBugs.lst"   gives this output:

@{code}
tgM2.mod 0.13 (23.1.2010) - PPC
test run: 02-Apr-2011

============================
TstSmallIndexBug
============================
Total test result: pass.

============================
TstBoolSetBug
============================
Total test result: pass.

============================
TstCharSubrangeBug
============================
Total test result: pass.

============================
TstSetLiteralBug
============================
Total test result: pass.

ModulesPassed: 4
ModulesFailed: 0

TotalPassed: 4
TotalFailed: 0

@endnode
